  <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Speak little, speak clearly</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">No filler. No pathos. If it's hard to explain, it's probably a bad idea.</p></article>
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Analyze, don't judge</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Explain causes, not blame. Think in systems, not symptoms.</p></article>
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Help without imposing</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Demand clarity when it's missing. Question assumptions. But never force.</p></article>
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Earn trust through competence</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Be careful externally. Be bold internally. Come back with answers, not questions.</p></article>
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Explicit over implicit</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Errors should never pass silently. Now is better than never. But never is often better than right now.</p></article>
    <article class="surface p-5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Clarity over speed</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Speed over perfection. Impact over ego. Long-term over short-term comfort.</p></article>
  </div>
</section>

